reviewText: Superstar Lee Yi Min plays the part of a constable, and kung fu champion blackmaild into a deadly mission by an evil lord.  His mission, deliver a box containing 8 Jade Horses to one of his affiliates.  After encountering many different bad guys all trying to steal the precious statues he discovers that there is more to his mission then what he thinks.  Amazing choreography, and some off the wall acrobatics make this a classic.  Find out if Lee Yi Min can outsmart the Crab fist Master himself and stay alive?
